CHRISTOPHER P. LEE

Christopher P. Lee, aged 55, was appointed as a Non- Executive Director in October 2013. He was reelected as a Director at the Seventeenth AGM of the Company held in November 2015. He has more than 31 years of business experience in the medical devices industry with experience in blue chip, SMEs and start- up companies. Mr. Lee holds an EMBA from Cranfield University.
